---
title: Beef Bulgogi Bowls with Pickled Cucumber & Sriracha Crema
description: This hearty bowl highlights Asian-inspired umami flavors and centers around ground pork browned and simmered in a savory miso-based ginger sauce with nutty sesame seeds. There’s also crisp quick-pickled cucumbers, tender sautéed cabbage and carrots, and spicy crema, all served over fluffy rice. And believe it or not, it’s ready on the table in just 20 minutes (or approximately 7 K-pop songs).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-bulgogi-bowls-e73f6513.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64d3d23b068f1d8d92df49bd.pdf
